snippet.title: Baby Dino Adventures BGA 2020 Trailer
snippet.description:
#babydinoadventures #babydino #BelgianGameAwards

This is the Baby Dino Adventures trailer that was broadcasted live at the Belgian Game Awards event on February, 21 2020

It showcases a few gameplay images of the upcoming demo that I will release in a few weeks
Game is still under active development, and should be released in 2021 on PC and Xbox (for now..)
More info on: https://twitter.com/__sleepingpanda

About Belgian Game Awards: https://awards.belgiangames.be
Related article (link in FR): http://www.press-start.be/2020/03/bga-2020-la-remise-des-prix/
